           perform   vis-tmo-cdp-des-000  thru vis-tmo-cdp-des-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice errato : reimpostazione           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-ycp-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tmo-cdp-100.
