      *                      * Test                                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-cdn-cdp-out-flg    =    spaces
                     go to pre-acc-ins-999.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ripristino numero protocollo            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-doc        to   w-att-cdp-prt-dat      .
           move      w-tes-cod-dpz        to   w-att-cdp-prt-dpz      .
           move      w-tes-num-prt        to   w-att-cdp-prt-num      .
