      *              * Max su [cdp], se non superato : a determinazio- *
      *              * ne finale                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-cdp-dat-doc       not  = w-tes-dat-doc or
                     rf-cdp-cod-dpz       not  = w-tes-cod-dpz or
                     rf-cdp-num-doc       not  = w-tes-num-doc
                     go to det-doc-ges-800.
       det-doc-ges-200.
