           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      70                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "             Pertanto il numero documento impostat
      -              "o non puo' es-      "
                                          to   v-alf                  .
